The purpose of this patch is to simplify the receive_mergeable().
Separate all the logic of XDP into a function.

Signed-off-by: Xuan Zhuo <xuanzhuo@linux.alibaba.com>
Acked-by: Jason Wang <jasowang@redhat.com>
